description:
It never rains but it pours. Amazon's long-awaited teaser for Rings of Power Season 2 finally released, and got promptly destroyed. Doctor Who released some of the worst episodes of TV ever created, and nobody celebrated the announcement that Phoebe Waller-Bridge's Tomb Raider show has been officially greenlit. Join me, MauLer, Gary, Shadiversity, Ryan Kinel and Despot of Antrim at the Open Bar. 

Subscribe to Nerdrotic: https://www.youtube.com/@nerdrotic
Subscribe to Shadiversity: https://www.youtube.com/@shadiversity
Subscribe to Ryan Kinel: https://www.youtube.com/@ryankinel-rkoutpost1
Subscribe to Despot: https://www.youtube.com/@DespotofAntrim
title: Open Bar #95 - Rings Of Power Demolished, Doctor Who Disaster, Fleabag Takes On Tomb Raider
